name: RR'uruurrr
Lore: 'Tusken Raider who tends to the banthas used by URoRRuR''R''R''s tribe. Expert in wielding a gaffi stick. Attacked Luke Skywalker in the Jundland Wastes.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. Power +3 while armed with a Gaderffi Stick. Where present, each of your banthas is power and forfeit +2 unless a Weequay is at a related site. When ''riding'' a bantha, adds one battle destiny.',
